Name: Average time for Accepted + In Progress when followed by Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Total time for Accepted + In Progress in variants that include Completed + In Call
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Minimum time for Accepted + In Progress in cases that transition to Completed + In Call within the same case
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Average duration of Accepted + In Progress compared to the duration of Completed + In Call in shared traces
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Time from the start of Accepted + In Progress to the start of Completed + In Call in variants where both activities occur consecutively or with intermediate steps
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Elapsed time between the last occurrence of Accepted + In Progress and the first occurrence of Completed + In Call in each case
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Cycle time of Accepted + In Progress in variants ending with Completed + In Call versus variants ending with Completed + Resolved
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Average time for Accepted + In Progress in variants that contain at least one Completed + In Call activity
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Total resolution time contribution of Accepted + In Progress in high-frequency variants featuring Completed + In Call
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Duration of Accepted + In Progress in variants where Completed + In Call appears as an intermediate resolution step before final closure

Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs
